,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"係時候搭車去維園了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴盈利跌12.9% 稅後盈利1.677 億元<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1474988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1474988</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc6e8c34c9b904530675ccdb84eb7a0abe12940a","tid":1481464,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68334670_10157948933987448_3981074593333903360_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_oc=AQm5AiFuqQrtIgJccfI1K86hTXuR4Kz1B0kQb2_MTu0EXpx3yZBQ4YyH7GrM5euQOfI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=758b1e5a4e2e1bcb9dcc24800cc4a87e&amp;oe=5DC8513B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68334670_10157948933987448_3981074593333903360_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_oc%3DAQm5AiFuqQrtIgJccfI1K86hTXuR4Kz1B0kQb2_MTu0EXpx3yZBQ4YyH7GrM5euQOfI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D758b1e5a4e2e1bcb9dcc24800cc4a87e%26oe%3D5DC8513B&h=d67099f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}